Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.18,0:00:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 打工的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.30,0:00:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快起床了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八軒同學 每天五點起床會不會很累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的 馬術社都是四點起床
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.97,0:00:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那明天開始就四點起床吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.26,0:00:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.80,0:00:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該死 打工的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.46,0:00:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別以為憑藉那種工作態度就能博得我的認同
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.85,0:00:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.21,0:00:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 打工的 來搬這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.62,0:00:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.66,0:00:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來修理這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.99,0:00:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.59,0:00:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來收拾這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.01,0:00:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗚… 這打工小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.14,0:00:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 礙事
